#| msgctxt "mp/game/combined_arms/rules"
#| msgid ""
#| "Domination\n"
#| "\n"
#| "In Domination, your goal is to capture and hold key positions on the map, "
#| "marked by flags. Whichever team that currently holds the greater number "
#| "of flags will gain points over time, and once a team reaches the target "
#| "number of points, they will win the game. Flags can only be captured by "
#| "infantry (excluding tank crew), within the circular boundary of a flag "
#| "zone.\n"
#| "\n"
#| "\n"
#| "\"CP\"\n"
#| "\n"
#| "Command Points determine the maximum number of troops a player can field "
#| "at any point during the game.\n"
#| "\n"
#| "\n"
#| "\"MP\"\n"
#| "\n"
#| "Manpower is the resource used by players to call new troops onto the "
#| "battlefield. The total amount of Manpower distributed throughout the game "
#| "is determined by the host, and once the battle has begun, players will "
#| "receive a steady income of Manpower until this limit has been reached. "
#| "Units lost will have their purchase price refunded to the player over "
#| "time, though again, the total amount of usable manpower will never exceed "
#| "the limit set by the host."
msgctxt "mp/game/combined_arms/rules"
msgid ""
"Combined Arms\n"
"\n"
"In Combined Arms, your goal is to capture and hold key positions on the map, "
"marked by flags. Whichever team that currently holds the greater number of "
"flags will gain points over time, and once a team reaches the target number "
"of points, they will win the game. Flags can only be captured by infantry "
"(excluding tank crew), within the circular boundary of a flag zone.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\"CP\"\n"
"\n"
"Command Points determine the maximum number of troops a player can field at "
"any point during the game.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\"MP\"\n"
"\n"
"Manpower is the resource used by players to call new troops onto the "
"battlefield. The total amount of Manpower distributed throughout the game is "
"determined by the host, and once the battle has begun, players will receive "
"a steady income of Manpower until this limit has been reached. Units lost "
"will have their purchase price refunded to the player over time, though "
"again, the total amount of usable manpower will never exceed the limit set "
"by the host."
msgstr "Armas combinadas\n\nArmas combinadas es un modo en el que el objetivo es ocupar y mantener los puntos estratégicos del mapa, señalados con banderas. Cada bandera ocupada otorga puntos a tu equipo. El primer equipo que alcance la puntuación preestablecida se alzará con la victoria. Solo las unidades de infantería pueden izar la bandera de tu equipo: son ellas las que deben completar la captura de las posiciones estratégicas.\n\n\n\"CP\"\n\nLos puntos de control determinan el número de unidades que un jugador puede tener a su mando durante la partida.\n\n\n\"MP\"\n\nLos puntos de mando permiten al jugador reclutar tropas. El número total de puntos de mando que recibe cada jugador está establecido por el anfitrión. A lo largo de la partida, cada jugador recibe de forma continua los puntos de mando asignados hasta que se alcanza el límite fijado por el anfitrión. El coste en puntos de mando de las tropas caídas en combate se recupera con el tiempo, pero nunca superará el límite fijado por el anfitrión."

